&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="out-of-office-hours-emergency-only"&gt;Out of office hours (emergency only)&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Applications for urgent emergency ad-hoc flights or last minute substitution flights that need to be made out of office hours, weekends and public holidays should be submitted to the Department for Transport Duty Office:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
